# UI Rules

## Brief introduction
These rules enforce the ANSVK UI system so generated screens stay consistent. Use approved components, tokenized styles, and standard ERP layout patterns.

- Use App* components from `lib/ui/components/`
- No hardcoded color literals in feature code; use tokens/theme
- Follow page patterns documented in `docs/ui/10 Page patterns.md`
- Component API expectations documented in `docs/ui/8 Component contracts.md`
- Keep Riverpod + go_router conventions from `docs/ui/9 Flutter UI conventions.md`
